Theyre experienced they have a great outside hitter  the transfer that came in from Syracuse Rackham Watt said PERIOD Theyre big in the middle they have an experienced Libero PERIOD Their freshman setter is doing a great job PERIOD Theyre really good at every position and theyre pretty experienced at every position PERIOD So theyre a tough battle. as a team Florida is hitting . and has  kills PERIOD Syracuse transfer Marina Markova has  kills for Florida which is second on the team PERIOD The 6foot5 outside hitter is hitting . on the year PERIOD Sophomore Merritt Beason leads the Gators with  kills on the year PERIOD She is swinging . for Florida PERIOD

The biggest thing for us will be the servepass Rackham Watt said PERIOD I know thats pretty much always the answer but were going to have to win the serving and passing battle. offensively Tennessee is led by senior Morgahn Fingall and sophomore Erykah Lovett PERIOD Fingall is swinging . for the Lady Vols with  kills PERIOD Lovett has  kills hitting . pERIOD
